{"tid":1893141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「老人屠夫」新病毒東京的一名高級保健機構員工因嚴重感染而住院","createTime":"2020-02-23T04:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T06:28:14.000Z","uid":33359,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe83418857910167781e74e9df11ea4bd6a06c20","tid":1893141,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200222/k10012297481000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fhtml%2F20200222%2Fk10012297481000.html&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAynqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=f7cf05bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200222/k10012297481000.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1582432728.A.658.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1582432728.A.658.html&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAynqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=839371c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1582432728.A.658.html</a><br />\n看了一下這消息還沒有在台灣公佈。<br />\n<br />\n東京都22日發表在東京都內的老人保健設施工作的60多歲男性職員感染<br />\n新型冠狀病毒的消息。<br />\n<br />\n該男住在東京內，這個12日雖然出現類似感冒的症狀到醫院看病，卻沒有<br />\n被診斷為肺炎而回家了，接著13日去老人保健設施上班。<br />\n（又一個生病跑去上班的例子....日本完全沒在管的嘛）<br />\n<br />\n14號在自己家裡過，15號跟全家一起到印尼旅行。<br />\n<br />\n歸國之後19日到都內的醫院住院，因為呼吸困難而住到ICU裡面。<br />\n<br />\n目前正在調查他在都內的路徑，包括他所工作的養老院中的人在內，密集<br />\n接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n包括此病例在內，在東京都內的確診人數達到29人。<br />\n<br />\n以上為新聞內容。<br />\n<br />\n根據其他的Twitter，他是養老院的駕駛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nwity55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fnwity55.png&h=3f8c46dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e416edbda510d7ed080872be36e44c8bef387043","tid":1893141,"uid":316420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />印尼旅行"},{"pid":"3dace99e69633cade1a12e091cf69f665b962ec2","tid":1893141,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"點解印仔post 左30分鐘都冇人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd58ad6bbe5a29b7ce7bd95e709dab43c68ae06","tid":1893141,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dace99e69633cade1a12e091cf69f665b962ec2","tid":1893141,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"點解印仔post 左30分鐘都冇人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"冇定"},{"pid":"4f849219c305268665cb06fb4ebeb0122c73981e","tid":1893141,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"印尼確診個案0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ade7b360d6c6be5b618935770c53b19015ea49c","tid":1893141,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"真係要毒死百幾件日本人先得<br />\n日本人而家仲豬過港豬"},{"pid":"3adff1601b300376bf98288c8f1516fca9f2529b","tid":1893141,"uid":30468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"日本仔一直都WFC<br />\n係咪想用武肺解決日本人口老化問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ed5af249ac398bde83fad25eb4b5add652d958","tid":1893141,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"60歲做老人院<br />\n老人照顧老人"}]}